# This file lives inside the workspace; it does NOT control the rendered gazette.
# The board is a sibling of the workspace (e.g. <repo>/board/), so it is ignored at the
# REPO ROOT .gitignore — `bureau:init` adds the board dir there. Nothing inside the
# workspace needs ignoring by default; the cabinets and logbook are committed.
#
# Recursion engine (ADR-0001): the decision log `_log.jsonl` is the SOURCE OF TRUTH and the
# trust ledgers `_verify.json` / `_compile-state.json` summarize decisions — all committed.
# `_gate.json` is the MECHANICAL-DERIVED cache: a pure function of (snapshot + log), rebuilt
# by `gazette fsck` to a byte-fixpoint, so it is regenerable and not committed.
_gate.json
